'''Kodama-hiko no Mikoto''' (児玉彦命) is a {{ill|kami|ja|神 (神道)|qq=draft}} worshiped in the {{ill|Suwa Region|ja|諏訪地方|qq=draft}} of {{ill|Nagano Prefecture|ja|長野県|qq=draft}}, as part of the {{ill|Suwa Faith|ja|諏訪信仰|qq=draft}}.

== Overview ==
[[File:Moriya Family Tree - 守矢氏系図.png|170px|thumbnail|{{Center|The first five generations of the {{ill|Moriya clan|ja|守矢氏|1=Moriya clan|qq=draft}} as depicted in the genealogical text}}]]
According to the {{ill|Kaminaga Moriya clan Genealogy|ja|神長守矢氏系譜|qq=draft}}, a genealogy of the {{ill|Moriya clan|ja|守矢氏|1=Moriya clan|qq=draft}} compiled in the early {{ill|Meiji Period|ja|明治時代|qq=draft}}:

<blockquote> {{ill|Oogami|ja|大神|qq=draft}}’s child, {{ill|Katakurabe no Mikoto|ja|片倉辺命|qq=draft}}, begot Kodama-hiko no Mikoto, who succeeded the position of {{ill|Chikatojin|ja|千鹿頭神|1=Chikatō-no-Kami|qq=draft}} in accordance with the divine words of Oogami. He married Mitutama-hime no Kami, the daughter of Moritatsu no Kami, and they bore Yatsukushin.<ref name="suwa">{{Cite book |title=Kaminaga Moriya clan Genealogy|author=Suwa Educational Association|year=1938|page=34|url=https://dl.ndl.go.jp/info:ndljp/pid/1185913/24}}</ref><ref name="tikatousin">[http://yatsu-genjin.jp/suwataisya/sanpo/tikatousin.htm Chikatojin (Genealogy of Moreya Clan)]</ref>
</blockquote>

As such, Kodama-hiko no Mikoto is regarded as the fourth generation in the genealogy of the Moriya clan.<ref name="tikatousin"/><ref>『続・高部の文化財』高部歴史編纂委員会編、2006th year 、31頁</ref>

== Genealogy ==
Kodama-hiko no Mikoto is the child of {{ill|Katakurabe no Mikoto|ja|片倉辺命|qq=draft}}, though his mother is unknown. His spouse, Mitutama-hime no Kami, the daughter of Moritatsu no Kami, bore him Yatsukushin, who is regarded as the fifth generation in the Moriya clan’s genealogy.<ref name="suwa"/>

== Shrines ==
Kodama-hiko no Mikoto is enshrined in the following locations:
* {{ill|Kodama-ishi Shrine|ja|児玉石神社|qq=draft}} (Yuno-waki, {{ill|Suwa City|ja|諏訪市|qq=draft}}, Nagano Prefecture)
* {{ill|Taisan Shrine|ja|泰山神社|qq=draft}} ({{ill|Takamori Town|ja|高森町|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Shimoina District|ja|下伊那郡|qq=draft}}, Nagano Prefecture)

== See Also ==
